title: myDC123.1
characteristics_ch1.2: antibodies: CD3:- CD14:- BDCA2:- BDCA1:+ CD123:+
extract_protocol_ch1.1: PBMCs were isolated with Ficoll Density Gradient
extract_protocol_ch1.2: RNA was isolated from two biological repliates (RNAeasy plus micro kit, QIagen)
extract_protocol_ch1.3: RNA libraries were prepared for sequencing using standard Illumina protocols
data_processing: Sequence reads were alligned using the R Subread aligner
data_processing.1: Genewise counts were obtained using FeatureCounts
data_processing.2: Counts were converted to counts per million mapped reads per kilobase of transcript
data_processing.4: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: raw_counts file is the counts as given by FeatureCounts
data_processing.5: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: norm_Log2RPKM files give the normalized Log2 reads per kilobase of transcript, per million mapped reads

extract_protocol_ch1.3: RNA libraries were prepared for sequencing using standard Illumina protocols
data_processing: Sequence reads were alligned using the R Subread aligner
data_processing.1: Genewise counts were obtained using FeatureCounts
data_processing.2: Counts were converted to counts per million mapped reads per kilobase of transcript
data_processing.4: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: raw_counts file is the counts as given by FeatureCounts
data_processing.5: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: norm_Log2RPKM files give the normalized Log2 reads per kilobase of transcript, per million mapped reads
